Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.38,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...keep thinking about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.29,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.68,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,When I was really little,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:06.92,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,there were nights when I couldn't get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:10.79,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,At times like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.85,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Mom would soothe me by patting my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I swear it was somewhere in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.21,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:55.98,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,When I was a little kid, without him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.10,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.44,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,You're the one who forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:12.88,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,First thing tomorrow morning, we'll ask the bus company. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.96,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,What a troublesome child you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.84,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Just like my mom did for me that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.34,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,if I could give something to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.41,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,maybe this feeling would go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.41,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Is what I found myself thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.18,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.52,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Or is she the innocent child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this yours, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't just come into my room like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You treasure such a cute teddy bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that I'm treasuring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You washed it and cleaned it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that wasn't... what I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that way of drying isn't nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want it, I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mom made it for me when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really make a difference if you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom made one for made it for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll keep this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so take care of that one, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't bully it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.56,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,She is definitely a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.84,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,...so I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.24,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'd like to think but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came during third period?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I woke up, the morning show was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I should have just come in the afternoon, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should've just taken the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually benefited from coming late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw this really cute guy on the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was tall, and fair skinned
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with really nice hair and really long eye lashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was probably a high school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was wearing a school uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At such an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The point?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so late,  but he was on the same train car
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on the same train at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sort of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it? Isn't it? I feel a romance coming on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Romance...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Loser buys drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, because I'm going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a life saver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't look so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, you're taking tomorrow off too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a compensatory day off from last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't Wakanai-san's arranged marriage meeting tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoot, I completely forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll come after lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can take the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he extremely shy in front of strangers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that he won't get nervous, we have to start from that meeting room,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then go to a nearby cafe, then go to a European restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't leave such an important job
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to someone who's been in a daze all the time lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, there you go lost in thought again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, go get some rest tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That cute guy you were talking about earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what school does he go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish I could've found that out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never seen his uniform before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the all-boys school that was established last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he was on the same train as you today
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's a chance you could see him again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to see what he looks like too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that blonde guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my god! Can I believe in fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the guy from this morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you think he's good-looking too right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to take a better look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Tamaki, right? He was kissing Tamaki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl! She said she wasn't interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make her spill it all out tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that medicine for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a pain reliever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go lie down in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is Nanoka all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was probably up late yesterday or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:53.01,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It looks like the beginning of the rainy season.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:57.04,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,The weather in the Kantou region isn't very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:01.78,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,There won't be any rain from tonight to tomorrow morning, but
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.67,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,it will most likely rain tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.72,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Please don't forget to bring your umbrella when you go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:12.20,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Next, tomorrow's weather for each area on Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:16.07,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,It will be cloudy followed by rain in Tokyo city.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.15,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Probability of precipitation in the morning is 60%
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.56,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,In the afternoon it will be 70%...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? You're not feeling well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just have really bad menstrual cramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First time in three months?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The doctor told me it's common for girls my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you worry even though I'm not really sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go to the convenience store on the way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Don't force yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you're over-exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw my friend kissing a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'm going to kiss someone someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have you explain everything about yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In junior high. We went to the same cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cram school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something that is unrelated to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.77,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,I said something weird last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.43,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan's probably used to kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:25.74,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,He's an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:32.52,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,When will I become an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't there any good love rolling around?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll probably stop soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:45.23,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,When you're in love, even boring things make your heart jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:48.42,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,That's what makes it really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.47,Dialogue - Italic,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no... it's gotten worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:21.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you come to pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was on my way to the store because I ran out of tobacco.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true! I only brought one umbrella too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:21.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your stomach ache?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you smiling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:15.61,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}I feel this way for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:20.57,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}A ray of sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:29.67,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}was suddenly cast into my saddened heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:35.61,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}Walking alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:40.61,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}I looked up at the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.61,0:00:44.65,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}and saw spring was near.{just adding words in here because I'm professional like that}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:48.68,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}It showed me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:53.82,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}these trembling feelings are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:58.97,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}like whirling petals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.97,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}Is it okay for me to fall in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:08.68,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:13.71,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}My hesitating heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:19.10,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}puts on the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:22.49,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}It’s so painful,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:33.72,OP - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}I can’t breathe.
