Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:40.61,OP - Jpk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}空みあげた時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.61,0:00:44.65,OP - Jpk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}春がそこに来てた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:48.68,OP - Jpk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}見せてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:53.82,OP - Jpk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}焦がれる想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:58.97,OP - Jpk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}舞い散る花びらね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.97,OP - Jpk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}好きになっていいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:08.68,OP - Jpk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}それとも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:13.71,OP - Jpk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}ためらう心が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:19.10,OP - Jpk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}ブレーキかけるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:22.49,OP - Jpk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}苦しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:33.72,OP - Jpk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}息が止まりそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.65,0:21:52.45,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}A gentle dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:58.48,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}calls the spring in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:04.38,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}and becomes a gentle breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:09.85,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}that touches you, then leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:12.94,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}In the small pot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:15.34,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}are feelings of love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:17.92,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}swaying softly.{dancing}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:21.17,ED - Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)}They carry a sweet scent,
